(116, 'Printing an Article', 'Once you have an article to print, choose&nbsp;<em><strong>print</strong></em>, and then click on <b><i>Print using system dialog</i></b>:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_jcaldwel/print1.jpg" style="width: 224px; height: 268px;" /><br />\nThen select&nbsp;<em><strong>Library_CASH_BW_Public on offset</strong></em>:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_jcaldwel/print2.jpg" style="width: 311px; height: 266px;" /><br />\nWhen you&#39;ve clicked&nbsp;<em><strong>print</strong></em>, go to the Reference Desk to ask the librarian to release the article.', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
(117, 'Search Academic Search Premier', '1. &nbsp;Enter your terms in the search boxes.\n<ul>\n	<li>Phrases of two or more words should be in quotation marks: &nbsp;<em>&quot;slam poetry&quot; &nbsp;&quot;performance poetry&quot;</em></li>\n	<li>If there are two or more&nbsp;terms for a concept, enter both, separated with OR: &nbsp;<em>race OR ethnicity</em></li>\n	<li>To search for alternative endings, put an&nbsp;askerisk after the root: &nbsp;<i>poe*</i> for&nbsp;<em>poet, poem&nbsp;</em>or&nbsp;<em>poetry</em>,&nbsp;<em>ethnic&nbsp;</em>for&nbsp;<em>ethnic&nbsp;</em>or&nbsp;<em>ethnicity</em>.</li>\n</ul>\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_jcaldwel/ASP.jpg" style="width: 620px; height: 430px;" /><br />\n2. &nbsp;To retrieve ONLY academic articles, click <i>Scholarly (Peer Reviewed) Journals</i>.<br />\n3. &nbsp;If the full text is not supplied in the database, click&nbsp;<em>Search for Article</em> to see if it&#39;s available elsewhere through the Library&#39;s resources.', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
