(224, 'World of Books', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>1. Introduction to Drew Library</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.drew.edu/library/about/general/library-map" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Map</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.drew.edu/library/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Library Webpage</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="https://librarycat.drew.edu/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Catalog</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.drew.edu/library/research/databases-by-title-a-z" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Databases</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>2. Transitions</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www-lib.nearnorthschools.ca/dewey/ddc.htm" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Dewey</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.loc.gov/catdir/cpso/lcco/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">LC</a></li>\n	<li>Print to electronic\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.escholarship.org/editions/view?docId=ft7w10086w&amp;brand=ucpress" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">A free online scholarly book</a>&nbsp;(also in print)</li>\n		<li>A purchased book in print and electronic form [e.g.&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://fordham.universitypressscholarship.com/view/10.5422/fso/9780823227457.001.0001/upso-9780823227457" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Ecospirit</a>]</li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.relegere.org/index.php/bct/index" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">A free online-only scholarly journal</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://religion-compass.com/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">An online-only subscription journal</a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>3. Research Process</strong>: from Topic to Question to Thesis</p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://users.drew.edu/Erubinst/researchpapers.htm" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">A one-page overview</a></li>\n	<li>Print guides\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li>Badke, Bill.&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.amazon.com/Research-Strategies-Finding-through-Information/dp/1462010172/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1307116265&amp;sr=1-1" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Research Strategies: Finding Your Way Through the Information Fog</a><em>.</em>&nbsp;New York: iUniverse, 2011.</li>\n		<li>Pazmino, Robert W.&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/search/ref=sr_adv_b/?search-alias=stripbooks&amp;unfiltered=1&amp;field-keywords=&amp;field-author=pazmino&amp;field-title=doing+theological+research&amp;field-isbn=&amp;field-publisher=&amp;node=&amp;field-p_n_condition-type=&amp;field-feature_browse-bin=&amp;field-binding_browse-bin=&amp;field-subject=&amp;field-language=&amp;field-dateop=&amp;field-datemod=&amp;field-dateyear=&amp;sort=relevanceexprank&amp;Adv-Srch-Books-Submit.x=35&amp;Adv-Srch-Books-Submit.y=15" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Doing Theological Research</a>. Eugene, Oregon: Wipf &amp; Stock, 2009.</li>\n		<li>Vyhmeister, Nancy Jean.&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.amazon.com/Quality-Research-Papers-Students-Religion/dp/0310274400/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1274289785&amp;sr=1-1" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Quality Research Papers, for Students of Religion and Theology.</a>Zondervan, 2008&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n		<li>Core, Deborah.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.amazon.com/Seminary-Student-Writes-Deborah-Core/dp/0827234473/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1377884618&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=seminary+student+writes" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">The Seminary Student Writes</a>.&nbsp; St. Louis: Chalice, 2000.&nbsp;</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.drew.edu/writingstudies/writing-center" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Writing Center</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>4. Styles of Research by Area</strong>: Bible, Historical Studies, Theology/Philosophy, Religion &amp; Society, Liturgical Studies</p>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>5. Tools of the Trade</strong>: Encyclopedias, Bibliographies, Library catalogs, Periodical databases, Internet</p>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>6. Subject Encyclopedias</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li>Versus general encyclopedias (especially&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Wikipeida</a>)</li>\n	<li>What they supply: encirclements, names, open questions, bibliographies (key texts)</li>\n	<li>Online\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.oxfordreference.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/browse?btog=book&amp;pageSize=100&amp;sort=title" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Oxford Reference Online</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.credoreference.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/home.do" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Credo reference library</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://go.galegroup.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/ps/start.do?p=GVRL&amp;u=madi95127&amp;authCount=1" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Gale reference library</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.oxfordaasc.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/learning_center?display=0&amp;c=refworks" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Oxford African American Studies Center</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.ministrymatters.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/library/#/dpcc/9d7f6fbe8953eb96d67f315fd14e5836/introduction.html" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Ministry Matters</a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li>Finding the most useful, on-topic encyclopedias\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://refuniv.odyssi.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/cgi-bin/phtml?@landing.htm" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Reference Universe</a></li>\n		<li>Searching the&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="https://librarycat.drew.edu/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">catalog</a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Evaluating encyclopedias (example:&nbsp;<a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/download/attachments/23304374/Encyclopedia+critique.docx?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1369251287408" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Encyclopedia of the Reformation</a><em>)</em></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>7. Bibliography</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li>As genre: monograph,&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www1.crk.umn.edu/library/researchresources/CRK_CONTENT_119694.html" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">annotated bibliography</a>,&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://journal.atla.com/ojs/index.php/theolib/article/view/29/408" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">bibliographic essay</a></li>\n	<li>Example of bibliographic essay:\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li>Evans, Christopher H.&nbsp; &quot;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.amazon.com/Liberalism-without-Illusions-Christian-Tradition/dp/1602582084/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1276195537&amp;sr=1-1" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Selected Bibliography</a>.&quot;&nbsp; In&nbsp;<em>Liberalism without</em>&nbsp;<em>Illusions:</em><br />\n		<em>&nbsp;&nbsp; Renewing an American Christian Tradition</em>.&nbsp; Waco, Texas:Baylor University Press, 2010.</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>As addendum, bibliographic notes, reference lists</li>\n	<li>Finding them\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/journal/10.1111/%28ISSN%291749-8171" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Religion Compass</a></li>\n		<li>via&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://web.ebscohost.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/ehost/search/advanced?sid=82b95a51-1097-4b32-b873-a9cfb2fd3ea8%40sessionmgr14&amp;vid=1&amp;hid=9" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">ATLA</a></li>\n		<li><em><a class="external-link" href="http://web.ebscohost.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/ehost/detail?sid=82b95a51-1097-4b32-b873-a9cfb2fd3ea8%40sessionmgr14&amp;vid=9&amp;hid=9&amp;bdata=JnNpdGU9ZWhvc3QtbGl2ZSZzY29wZT1zaXRl#db=aph&amp;AN=89479241" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Chronicle of Higher Education</a></em></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>8. Library catalogs</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="https://librarycat.drew.edu/web2/tramp2.exe/log_in/guest?SETTING_KEY=English" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Drew&#39;s Catalog</a>\n\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li>Author and/or title searching</li>\n		<li>Subject searching (<a class="external-link" href="http://authorities.loc.gov/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">LCSH</a>)</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://newfirstsearch.oclc.org.ezproxy.drew.edu/WebZ/FSPrefs?entityjsdetect=:javascript=true:screensize=large:sessionid=fsapp6-40113-hlidk7m1-cfjxs4:entitypagenum=1:0" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Worldcat</a>\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li>Deeper searches of Drew Library</li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.drew.edu/library/ill" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Interlibrary loan</a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.drew.edu/library/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Summon</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>9.&nbsp; Online Books</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="https://www.google.com/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Google Books</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://site.ebrary.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/lib/drew/home.action" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Ebrary</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.oxfordscholarship.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/browse?t1=religion" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Oxford Scholarship Online</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://search.proquest.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/pqdthss/advanced?accountid=10558" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Dissertations and Theses</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>10.&nbsp; Evaluating Books</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://galenet.galegroup.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/servlet/GLD;jsessionid=5013A9D3D7B04042EC724BC890597798?locID=madi95127" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Contemporary Authors</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.google.com/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Google Books and Google Scholar</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://apps.webofknowledge.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/WOS_GeneralSearch_input.do?product=WOS&amp;search_mode=GeneralSearch&amp;SID=2BpDGabGh5igcHlHhiK&amp;preferencesSaved=" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Arts and Humanities Citation Index</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Publisher webpages, e.g.&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://bakerpublishinggroup.com/bakeracademic" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Baker Academic</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="https://www.ashgate.com/default.aspx?page=2561" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Ashgate</a></li>\n	<li>Book reviews\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://web.ebscohost.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/ehost/detail?sid=c3949d50-cedf-4c14-9da4-89f9baf43e02%40sessionmgr10&amp;vid=4&amp;hid=10&amp;bdata=JnNpdGU9ZWhvc3QtbGl2ZSZzY29wZT1zaXRl#db=rfh&amp;jid=ATLA0000003490" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Religious Studies Review</a></li>\n		<li>via&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://web.ebscohost.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/ehost/search/advanced?sid=67061c6d-5e2a-46a9-a79b-609092e0fb73%40sessionmgr11&amp;vid=1&amp;hid=9" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">ATLA</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.amazon.com/Kant-Biography-Manfred-Kuehn/dp/0521524067/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1274375571&amp;sr=1-1" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Amazon</a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>11. Citing Books</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.chicagomanualofstyle.org.ezproxy.drew.edu/16/contents.html" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Chicago Manual of Style&nbsp;</a>and the&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.chicagomanualofstyle.org/CMS_FAQ/Documentation/Documentation_questions01.html" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Manual of Style Q&amp;A page</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Some guides to Chicago style\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li>From&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://writing.wisc.edu/Handbook/DocChicago.html" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Wisconsin-Madison</a>&nbsp;</li>\n		<li>From&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.uwp.edu/departments/library/guides/pdf_guides/turabian.pdf" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Wisconsin-Parkside</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n		<li>From&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.bridgew.edu/library/styleman.cfm" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Bridgewater State University</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class="external-link" href="http://www.press.uchicago.edu/books/turabian/turabian_citationguide.html" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Turabian</a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
