text-decoration: none;">Government Documents: GPO Access</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.census.gov/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Census Bureau</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://statab.conquestsystems.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/sa/?id=16b44756-64a3-4d34-b479-22af810cbacf" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Statistic Abstract of the U.S.</a>&nbsp;(<a class="external-link" href="http://www.census.gov/compendia/statab/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">alternative site</a>)</li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.bjs.gov/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Bureau of Justice Statistics</a></li>\n		<li>Bureau of Labor Statistics</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Religion Statistics\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.thearda.com/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">ARDA</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.adherents.com/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Adherents.com</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://livinginliminality.files.wordpress.com/2009/03/aris_report_2008.pdf" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">American Religious Identification&nbsp;Survey</a></li>\n		<li><em>Yearbook of American and Canadian Churches</em>&nbsp;[BR13.Y4, Reference Counter]</li>\n		<li><em>2010 U.S. Religious Census&nbsp;</em>&nbsp;[BL2525 .A15] [<a class="external-link" href="http://i.imgur.com/zFm0U.png" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">sample page</a>]</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<strong>Useful Websites</strong>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong><a href="http://hirr.hartsem.edu/sociology/sociology.html">http://hirr.hartsem.edu/sociology/sociology.html</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></li>\n	<li><strong>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.religionandnature.com/">http://www.religionandnature.com/</a> &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><strong>Searching the Internet</strong></p>\n\n<ul style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.google.com/advanced_search" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Google</a>&nbsp;(use Advanced, and employ limiters)</li>\n	<li>Classified indexes to web sites\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; list-style-type: disc;">\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.wabashcenter.wabash.edu/resources/guide_headings.aspx" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Wabash Center Guide</a></li>\n		<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.drew.edu/library/research/subject-databases" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Drew University Library guides by subject</a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://olinuris.library.cornell.edu/ref/research/webeval.html" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Evaluating web sites</a></li>\n	<li><a class="external-link" href="http://www.uwp.edu/departments/library/guides/pdf_guides/turabian.pdf" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(50, 108, 166); text-decoration: none;">Citing web sites</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
