(435, 'Summon search', '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">Summon is a google-like search of Drew Library Resources. You can look for books that are in the Drew Library with Summon, &nbsp;as well &nbsp;as academic (peer-reviewed or scholarly) &nbsp;articles, newspapers and &nbsp;other resources, such as vetted public websites.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">Summon can be found on the <a href="http://www.drew.edu/library/research" target="_blank">Research Resources </a>page.&nbsp;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8000011444092px;">Type in keyword or phrase into the Summon box:</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8000011444092px;"><img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/summon_health_inequality.png" style="width: 517px; height: 93px;" /><br />\n​After searching, you will get lots of options to narrow &nbsp;your search. Some key limits are:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/summon_filters.png" style="width: 214px; height: 543px;" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">The more....button provides subtopics for your major topic. It&#39;s a very useful option because it helps to narrow your focus,</span>', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
