(438, 'Background', 'When you need quick information or background material, start with a relevant subject encyclopedia such as:<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{1145}, {Concise Encyclopedia of Latin American Literature, 2000.},{01}}<br />\n{{dab},{1146}, {Encyclopedia of Latin American and Caribbean Literature, 1900-2003, 2004.},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{1082}, {Encyclopedia of Literary and Cultural Theory, 2011.},{00}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{1301}, {Encyclopedia of Contemporary Spanish Culture, 1999.},{01}}<br />\n{{dab},{1184}, {Encyclopedia of Latin American History and Culture, 2008},{01}}<br />\n{{dab},{1148}, {Greenwood Encyclopedia of Latino Literature, 2002.},{01}}<br />\n{{dab},{114}, {Oxford Encyclopedia of Latinos and Latinas in the United States},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{1147}, {Pop Culture Latin America! 2005.},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{1302}, {Spanish Culture and Society, 2002.},{01}}<br />\n&nbsp;', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
(440, 'Find books', '<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">{{dab},{16}, {Drew Library Catalog},{01}}</span><br />\n<br />\nDo a simple search using keywords, or browse subject headings related to your topic using the <strong>exact </strong>option.<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/exact_search.png" style="width: 345px; height: 370px;" /><br />\n<br />\nUse the drop down menu to select<strong> subjects</strong>:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/exact_african_americans_catalog.png" style="width: 616px; height: 67px;" /><br />\n<br />\nAnother relevant subject heading is:<strong> slavery</strong><br />\n<br style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;" />\n<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">{{dab},{94}, {Worldcat},{01}}</span>', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
(441, 'SUMMON', '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">SUMMON is a google-like search of Drew Library Resources. You can look for books that are in the Drew Library with Summon, &nbsp;as well &nbsp;as academic (peer-reviewed or scholarly) &nbsp;articles, newspapers and &nbsp;other resources, such as vetted public websites.</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">Summon can be found on the Research Resources page. &nbsp;</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 20.8000011444092px;">From&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.drew.edu/home/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139); text-decoration: none; border: 0px; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 20.8000011444092px;" target="_blank">Treehouse</a><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 20.8000011444092px;">, click on Research Resources:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/research_resources.png" style="width: 372px; height: 122px;" /></span><br />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8000011444092px;">Type in keyword or phrase:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/summon_health_inequality.png" style="width: 517px; height: 93px;" /></span><br />\n<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 20.8000011444092px;">After searching, you will get lots of options to narrow &nbsp;your search. Some key limits are:</span>\n<div style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px;">\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="filters" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0.7692em; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: top; border-spacing: 0px; zoom: 1; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);">\n	<tbody class="static" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; zoom: 1;">\n		<tr style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; zoom: 1;">\n			<td class="facetLabel" style="padding: 2px 0px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: top; zoom: 1;"><label for="facet:is_peer_reviewed" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; zoom: 1;"><span class="label" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; zoom: 1;">Limit to articles from peer-reviewed publications</span></label><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\n			<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; verti