(442, 'Full text', '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">If there is no link to the full text:&nbsp;</span><img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/html_pdf.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 36px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px; width: 379px;" /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">&nbsp;click on the article linker icon:&nbsp;</span><img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/article_linker.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 35px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px; width: 116px;" /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">.</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">If the full tex is available from another database, you&#39;ll get a screen with hyperlinks to the article:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/article_linker_results.png" style="width: 674px; height: 172px;" /><br />\nIf there are no hyperlinks to an article, click on &quot;Request and InterLibraryLoan&quot;:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/request_an_ILL.png" style="width: 364px; height: 124px;" /></span>', NULL, 0, 'Basic',