(463, 'Get full text', '<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">If there is no link to the full text:&nbsp;</span><img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/html_pdf.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 36px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px; width: 379px;" /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">&nbsp;click on the article linker icon:&nbsp;</span><img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/article_linker.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 35px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px; width: 116px;" /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">.</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">If the full tex is available from another database, you&#39;ll get a screen with hyperlinks to the article:</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/article_linker_results.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 172px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px; width: 674px;" /><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">If there are no hyperlinks to an article, click on &quot;Request and InterLibrarLoan&quot;:</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/request_an_ILL.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 124px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px; width: 364px;" /></p>\n\n<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 20px;"><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\nThe first time you request an article or book via InterLibraryLoan, you &nbsp;will &nbsp;be asked to fill out a short form.&nbsp;<b style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">It may take several days to receive an article via InterLibraryLoan; &nbsp;books can take longer.</b></p>\n', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
