(465, 'More places to search', '<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px;">From&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.drew.edu/home/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139); text-decoration: none; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 19.5px;" target="_blank">Treehouse</a><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 19.5px;">, click on Research Resources:<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/treehouse_research_resources.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 127px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; width: 363px;" /><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\nClick on List of Resources by Title (A-Z)<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_epatters/a-z_list.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 154px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; width: 496px;" /></span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;">Academic Search Premier is a good place to start your search. Also try ProQuest Research Library.</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/u