(571, 'Find scholarly articles', '<strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">PsycINFO is the primary database you will use for &nbsp;this class.</strong><br />\n<a href="http://ezproxy.drew.edu/login?url=http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=ip,uid&amp;profile=ehost&amp;defaultdb=psyh" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;" target="_blank">PsycINFO</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">&nbsp;</span><img alt="Restricted Resource" border="0" height="16" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/images/icons/lock.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px; height: auto !important;" title="Restricted Resource" width="16" /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">&nbsp;</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Indexes and abstracts the international journal, and book literature in psychology and related disciplines since 1887. Lots of full text is available. Click on the &quot;find article&quot; icon if the pdf or html link to the article is not visible.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Other relevant databases for this class include:</strong></span>\n<div class="dbresults no-border" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; border: none; clear: both; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;"><a href="http://ezproxy.drew.edu/login?url=http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=ip,uid&amp;profile=ehost&amp;defaultdb=byh" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139);" target="_blank">Biomedical Reference Collection: Comprehensive</a>&nbsp;<img alt="Restricted Resource" border="0" height="16" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/images/icons/lock.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px;" title="Restricted Resource" width="16" />&nbsp;<img alt="Some full text available" border="0" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/images/icons/full_text.gif" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px;" title="Some full text available" /><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\nMore medicine/medical focused, but still relevant for psychology. Lots of full text is available</div>\n\n<div class="dbresults" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; clear: both; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(223, 223, 223); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;"><a href="http://scholar.google.com/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139);" target="_blank">Google Scholar</a>&nbsp;<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\nThis free, interdisciplinary resource indexes the available text of&nbsp;<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">scholarly</strong>&nbsp;journal sites and scholarly website collections on the Internet, and allows citation searching. No subject searching.<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\nMake sure Scholar Preferences are set to include Library Links from Drew to check subscription content availability; some collections, however, are not linked.</div>\n\n<div class="dbresults" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; clear: both; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(223, 223, 223); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;"><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi" style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139);" target="_blank">PubMed</a><span style="font-size: 13.3333330154419px;">&nbsp;</span></div>\n\n<div class="dbresults" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; clear: both; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(223, 223, 223); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">PubMed comprises more than 23 million citations for biomedical literature from MEDLINE, life science journals, and online books. Citations may include links to full-text content from PubMed Central and publisher web sites, but do NOT include links to Drew-owned material</div>\n\n<div class="dbresults" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; clear: both; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(223, 223, 223); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;"><a href="http://ezproxy.drew.edu/login?url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=HomePageURL&amp;_method=userHomePage&amp;_acct=C000038258&amp;_version=1&amp;_urlVersion=0&amp;_userid=799667&amp;md5=cbd5dad2f4bb4d0ad6740592c26b1bdf" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139);" target="_blank">ScienceDirect</a>&nbsp;<img alt="Restricted Resource" border="0" height="16" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/images/icons/lock.png" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px;" title="Restricted Resource" width="16" />&nbsp;<img alt="Some full text available" border="0" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/images/icons/full_text.gif" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px;" title="Some full text available" /><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\nLarge interdisciplinary database containing lots of psychology and neuroscience journals.<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" />\n<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">note:&nbsp;</strong>To obtain full text ScienceDirect articles outside of Drew&#39;s subscribed content, please contact<a href="http://www.drew.edu/library/ask-a-librarian" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139); text-decoration: none;">Drew Library Chat</a>&nbsp;with citation information (Monday-Friday 9AM-5PM and Sun-Thursday 6PM-10PM) or submit article request through&nbsp;<a href="https://illiad.drew.edu/illiad/Logon.html" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139); text-decoration: none;">Inter-Library Loan</a>.&nbsp;<a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/pages/viewpage.action;jsessionid=BD7D1A0204BF023DBFEAF11ECFC6FB36?pageId=43909305" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 26, 139); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">Click here for instructions and more details.</a></div>\n', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
