(575, 'Does Drew own it?', 'If you are in a database <strong>other than PubMed,&nbsp;</strong>click on&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_jcaldwel/ArticleLinker.jpg" style="width: 72px; height: 18px;" /> to see if Drew owns or has access to an article you want.<br />\n<br />\nIf you are <strong>in PubMed</strong>, copy the article DOI or the PubMed ID, and paste it into the Journal List Search box:<br />\n<img alt="" src="http://walter.drew.edu/splus/assets/users/_jcaldwel/DOI.jpg" style="width: 757px; height: 312px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;" /><br />\n<br />\nIf you have a specific journal article that you&#39;ve found cited elsewhere:\n<ul>\n	<li>Enter the&nbsp;<strong>title of the journal</strong> (not the title of the article) into the Journal List Search, and locate the issue of the journal OR</li>\n	<li>Enter the title of the article in Summon. &nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\nIf you have a book that you need, first check the Drew Catalog, using&nbsp;<strong>Exact search</strong>.<br />\n<br />\nIf the article or book is not accessible at Drew, request it through <a href="http://www.drew.edu/library/ill">Interlibrary Loan</a>.', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
