(701, 'Finding Additional Information', 'If you need <strong>additional information</strong> beyond a fast definition or an overview, check either for books or for journal or magazine articles:<br />\n<br />\n<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;">{{dab},{2}, {SUMMON},{01}} Click on Advanced Search for more structured searching. &nbsp;Use the facets in the left column on the results page to help focus your search.</span><br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{16}, {Drew Library Catalog},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{4}, {Academic Search Premier},{01}}<br />\n<br />\nFor<strong> reviews</strong> of specific films, consult:<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{96}, {FIAF},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{1152}, {MRQE (Movie Review Query Engine)},{01}}<br />\n<br />\nFor issues pertaining to specific ethnic groups, check:<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{71}, {Ethnic Newswatch},{01}}<br />\nOn the first page of the database, scroll down to select the ethnic group.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
