(735, 'Books,  journals, and newspapers to browse', '<span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Library has access to a number of books, journals, and newspapers that focus on politics, which may be useful to browse. Access to some are restricted, meaning Drew login is required.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>&gt;Books</strong></span><br />\n<span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">Storey, William.</span><a href="http://site.ebrary.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/lib/drew/detail.action?docID=10402738" style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">&nbsp;Politics Study Guides : U.S. Government and Politics&nbsp;</a><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">(2nd Edition). Edinburgh, GBR: Edinburgh University Press, 2010. ProQuest ebrary.&nbsp;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Strahan, Randall. <a href="http://site.ebrary.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/lib/drew/detail.action?docID=10389801">Interpreting American Politics : Leading Representatives : The Agency of Leaders in the Politics of the U.S. House</a>. Baltimore, MD, USA: Johns Hopkins University Press, 2007. ProQuest ebrary.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>&gt;Journals</strong><br />\n<a href="http://search.proquest.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/publication/2029223">Politics and governance</a>, 2013 to present<br />\n<a href="http://pas.sagepub.com.ezproxy.drew.edu/content/by/year">Politics &amp; Society,</a> 1970 - present</span>\n<div class="SSJournalAlternateTitle" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif;"><br />\n<strong>&gt;<em>Newspapers</em></strong><br />\n{{dab},{76}, {LexisNexis Academic},{11}}<br />\n<br />\n<span style="font-