(749, 'Your Personal Librarian', 'Jody Caldwell is your Personal Librarian - available for help in finding resources, selecting reliable sources of information, and formatting your citations. &nbsp;For more information about the Personal Librarian program, check <a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=26509393">here</a>.', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
(750, 'Finding Background Information', '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px; line-height: 19.5px;">Encyclopedias, dictionaries or other reference sources can often give helpful overviews or definitions - if you run across a term you don&#39;t know, or if you want some quick background on a topic, check here.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">{{dab},{1151}, {Chambers Film Factfinder, 2006.},{01}}</span><br />\n{{dab},{51}, {Credo Reference},{01}}<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{362}, {IMDB: Internet Movie Database},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{1152}, {MRQE (Movie Review Query Engine)},{01}}', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
(752, 'Finding Additional Information', 'If you need additional information beyond a fast definition or an overview, check either for books or for journal or magazine articles on either films or their social contexts. &nbsp;Some general sources include:<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{16}, {Drew Library Catalog},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{4}, {Academic Search Premier},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{2}, {SUMMON},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Need more?</strong><br />\nYou can also check databases that focus on film, which may have more material than the general sources listed above:<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{96}, {FIAF},{01}} &nbsp;<br />\nUse the &quot;Film/TV title&quot; to find material on a particular film. &nbsp;Films are indexed by their original names: &nbsp;<em>The skin I live in</em> is found under&nbsp;<em>Piel que habito</em>.<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{97}, {Film Index International},{01}}<br />\n<br />\n{{dab},{98}, {International Index to the Performing Arts},{01}}', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
