(837, 'Finding Additional Information on Festivals', 'Check the databases above for analyses of film festivals. &nbsp;Be sure to include alternative terms: &nbsp;<em>&quot;pan-african film*&quot; OR fespaco</em> or&nbsp;<em>&quot;academy awards&quot; OR oscars</em>. &nbsp;For information on specific film festivals, often including links to the festival&#39;w websites, check:<br />\n<a href="http://www.festivalfocus.org/">FestivalFocus</a><br />\n<a href="http://www.filmfestivals.com/">Film Festivals.com</a><br />\n<a href="http://film.britishcouncil.org/festivals-directory">British Council Film Directory</a><br />\n&nbsp;', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
