(996, 'Citation help', '<strong style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">Electronic citation managment</strong><br style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;" />\n<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">{{dab},{1045}, {EndnoteWeb},{11}}</span><br style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;" />\n<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">(Beware: No citation software is perfect--check your work!) &nbsp;</span><a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/display/techdocs/Endnote+Web+Bibliographic+Software" style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;" target="_blank">Instructions for EndNote Web</a>\n<ul>\n	<li>Upcoming EndNote Workshops: check <a href="http://www.drew.edu/library/2016/01/endnote-webbasic-training-feb-22-24">HERE</a></li>\n</ul>\n<strong><span style="font-size: 13px;">Websites&nbsp;</span></strong><br />\n{{dab},{1175}, {Scientific Style and Format Citation Quick Guide },{11}}<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style="font-size: 13px;">Reference Books&nbsp;</span></strong><br />\n<span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">Lipson, Charles.&nbsp;</span><i style="zoom: 1; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">Doing Honest Work in College: How to Prepare Citations, Avoid Plagiarism, and Achieve Real Academic Success</i><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">. Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 2004. Print .</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: -webkit-center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">PN171 .F56 L56 2004</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">Drew University&#39;s plagiarism policy</strong><br style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;" />\n<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">Take time to familiarize yourself with Drew&#39;s policy on plagiarism. &nbsp;<a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/display/Handbook/Academic+Integrity+policy" target="_blank">CLICK HERE</a>&nbsp;for a link to&nbsp;the &quot;Academic Integrity&quot; section of Drew&#39;s Student Handbook which&nbsp;contains a&nbsp;description of the plagiarism policy.</span>', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
(997, 'Indications of Quality', 'Just like there are things you look for when buying a product in real life to determine whether it is of good quality, there are hints that suggest an information source may be good... or not good.<br />\n<br />\nTake a minute to think about what those hints are. Here&#39;s some words that may help:\n<ul>\n	<li>Currency</li>\n	<li>Analysis</li>\n	<li>Reputation</li>\n	<li>Subject expertise &amp;&nbsp;Education</li>\n	<li>Sources/Bibliography/References</li>\n	<li>Facts</li>\n	<li>Scholarship</li>\n	<li>Peer Review</li>\n</ul>\n', NULL, 0, 'Basic', '', 0, 0, NULL),
