(806, 'Islam and Islamic Studies Resources', '', 'For Muslims &amp; non-Muslims, this site links to primary sources (sacred texts, texts in Islamic law and schools of theology, contemporary documents) and scholarly secondary sources. Covers Islamic history, culture, and contemporary topics. By Alan Godlas (U of Georgia).', '', NULL, '2013-08-19 17:27:28', 0),
