(1189, 'PILOTS: Published International Literature On Traumatic Stress', '', 'From the National Center for PTSD, including &quot;<span style="color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 15px;">citations to all literature on post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) and other mental-health sequelae of traumatic events, without disciplinary, linguistic, or geographical limitations.&quot;</span>', '', NULL, '2015-03-04 00:17:04', 0),
