(1294, 'Defining Moments: The Harlem Renaissance', '', 'An introductory volume on this era, collecting a &quot;narrative overview,&quot; followed by biographies of 10 of the prominent figures, and finally some primary sources from authors such as Langston Hughes, W.E.B. Dubois, and Dorothy West.', '', NULL, '2015-09-01 20:40:42', 0),
